refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public boolDirectoryIterator::isExecutable
Determines if the current DirectoryIterator item is executable.

  &reftitle.examples;



    DirectoryIterator::isExecutable example


     This example lists files in the directory containing the script 
     which are executable.



<?php
$iterator = new DirectoryIterator(dirname(__FILE__));
foreach ($iterator as $fileinfo) {
    if ($fileinfo->isExecutable()) {
        echo $fileinfo->getFilename() . "\n";
    }
}
?>


